Scripts available

1) Create input files for aurora. Run
$  python3 make_input_xml.py
from either the uwuw-mats or legacy-mats directories (as appropriate for your choice of material treatment). Copy the created files and dagmc.h5m to the root aurora directory.

2) Run openmc in plotting mode: run
python3 make_input_and_plot.py
from either the uwuw-mats or legacy-mats directories (as appropriate for your choice of material treatment).

3) Run openmc
python3 make_input_and_plot.py
from either the uwuw-mats or legacy-mats directories (as appropriate for your choice of material treatment).

